                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Chief Steward Role</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>To be friendly and helpful to the general public at all times.</li>
                    <li>To take instruction from the Assistant Head and Head Stewards.</li>
                    <li>To manage a team of stewards in an allotted area.</li>
                    <li>To communicate any issues to Assistant Head / Head Steward if needed.</li>
                    <li>To ensure all stewards have breaks and that area is sufficiently covered.</li>
                    <li>To use radio provided to communicate with team as relevant.</li>
                    <li>To be aware of health and safety issues and report appropriately.</li>
                    <li>To be aware regarding of issues public safety and report any issues appropriately.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="StageCrewVolunteers" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
                <h3 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">StageCrewVolunteers</h3>
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Stage Crew Volunteers role and requirements.</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>As a volunteer for the construction of the stages and associated build of the festival it is of paramount importance that volunteers are physically capable and confident in manual labour.</p>

                <p>
                    Experience in event builds or similar trades/professions would be an advantage and any useful skills should be flagged up during the enrolment process.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Volunteers can expect to be fully briefed regarding health & safety, provided with relevant tools/kit/PPE (excluding steel toe capped boots) and led by an experienced member of the festival build team.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Volunteers should stipulate their availability for the build and strike down.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Flexibility is needed regarding this role as the logistics of a festival build/take down can be prone to alterations and changes, the enrolment form will ask for clarification on dates/times of volunteer availability.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <b>Duties will involve:</b>
                </p>

                <p>
                    Lifting, moving equipment, constructing stages, building and installing festival infrastructure, running cables, installing fences, basically constructing and then de constructing the physical furniture of the event.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Volunteers will be expected to be:
                </p>

                <p>
                    Physically fit and capable of manual work however no matter what your abilities we can utilise your skills.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Happy and willing to take instruction from an experienced team leader.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Conscious of the need to work safely and as a member of a team.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Flexible attitude towards the types of tasks to be undertaken (building stages/hanging back drops/erecting fencing/moving stuff etc).
                </p>

                <p>
                    Please provide your own steel toe capped boots as some tasks will require their use, if you do not have such boots then you will be assigned a task that does not require them.
                </p>

                <p>Volunteers are particularly needed for the “strike down” (de construction) of the event which happens from the moment the festival finishes and for several days afterwards so please let us know if your available.</p>

</div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="OnStage" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
