                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">On site catering job role</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>To work as part of a team.</li>
                    <li>To work in on-site kitchen providing breakfast, lunch and dinner for the crew.</li>
                    <li>To fulfil any duties as needed.</li>
                    <li>To assist in food preparation, serving and cleaning.</li>
                    <li>To work shifts.</li>
                    <li>To take direction from Shona, head of the kitchen.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-header">                
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">On-site catering assistant job specification</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <ul>
                    <li>To be available for varying shifts from Thursday 1st September – Sunday 4th September. (essential)</li>
                    <li>To be able to commit to at least 3 shifts. (essential)</li>
                    <li>To have experience working/training in a professional kitchen. (desirable)</li>
                    <li>To be reliable and a good time keeper. (essential)</li>
                    <li>To be flexible and adaptable to the needs of a festival kitchen. (essential)</li>
                    <li>To be able to work well in a team. (essential)</li>
                    <li>To have experience working front-of-house. (desirable)</li>
                    <li>To have a current food and hygiene certificate. (desirable)</li>
                    <li>To have experience working in an outside environment. (desirable)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

